{"author":"杳眇","author_url":"https://github.com/Hosuke","chapter_count":33,"id":"yaomiao-zhuangzi","intro":"杳眇注南華者，承帛書老子注之體，辨莊周本義與郭象注之異——尤於逍遙、齊物、坐忘、心齋諸關目，復其無待之旨。凡三十三篇——內七、外十五、雜十一——章三層：南華原文、古注要錄、杳眇注。疏之為體，文言不限字數，兼示內外雜之別、莊禪之通、俗讀之失、偽篇之辨（讓王、盜跖、說劍、漁父等）。引斯文文庫諸條為 [[wikilink]]，使讀者遊網而讀。","sections":[{"chapters":[{"chapter_no":1,"chapter_title":"第一篇 逍遙遊","id":"內-01","帛書_no":null,"王弼_no":null},{"chapter_no":2,"chapter_title":"第二篇 齊物論","id":"內-02","帛書_no":null,"王弼_no":null},{"chapter_no":3,"chapter_title":"第三篇 養生主","id":"內-03","帛書_no":null,"王弼_no":null},{"chapter_no":4,"chapter_title":"第四篇 人間世","id":"內-04","帛書_no":null,"王弼_no":null},{"chapter_no":5,"chapter_title":"第五篇 德充符","id":"內-05","帛書_no":null,"王弼_no":null},{"chapter_no":6,"chapter_title":"第六篇 大宗師","id":"內-06","帛書_no":null,"王弼_no":null},{"chapter_no":7,"chapter_title":"第七篇 應帝王","id":"內-07","帛書_no":null,"王弼_no":null}],"name":"內篇"},{"chapters":[{"chapter_no":1,"chapter_title":"第一篇 駢拇","id":"外-01","帛書_no":null,"王弼_no":null},{"chapter_no":2,"chapter_title":"第二篇 馬蹄","id":"外-02","帛書_no":null,"王弼_no":null},{"chapter_no":3,"chapter_title":"第三篇 胠篋","id":"外-03","帛書_no":null,"王弼_no":null},{"chapter_no":4,"chapter_title":"第四篇 在宥","id":"外-04","帛書_no":null,"王弼_no":null},{"chapter_no":5,"chapter_title":"第五篇 天地","id":"外-05","帛書_no":null,"王弼_no":null},{"chapter_no":6,"chapter_title":"第六篇 天道","id":"外-06","帛書_no":null,"王弼_no":null},{"chapter_no":7,"chapter_title":"第七篇 天運","id":"外-07","帛書_no":null,"王弼_no":null},{"chapter_no":8,"chapter_title":"第八篇 刻意","id":"外-08","帛書_no":null,"王弼_no":null},{"chapter_no":9,"chapter_title":"第九篇 繕性","id":"外-09","帛書_no":null,"王弼_no":null},{"chapter_no":10,"chapter_title":"第十篇 秋水","id":"外-10","帛書_no":null,"王弼_no":null},{"chapter_no":11,"chapter_title":"第十一篇 至樂","id":"外-11","帛書_no":null,"王弼_no":null},{"chapter_no":12,"chapter_title":"第十二篇 達生","id":"外-12","帛書_no":null,"王弼_no":null},{"chapter_no":13,"chapter_title":"第十三篇 山木","id":"外-13","帛書_no":null,"王弼_no":null},{"chapter_no":14,"chapter_title":"第十四篇 田子方","id":"外-14"